    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cookies are a bit different, but these cookie monsters love them! Start baking some cookies and watch as the monsters devour every crumb.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329020/extras/95ac3b1a4740f32ad62468c8e5756397.poster.avif?t=1733406088\" width=572 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329020/extras/95ac3b1a4740f32ad62468c8e5756397.webm?t=1733406088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329020/extras/95ac3b1a4740f32ad62468c8e5756397.mp4?t=1733406088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep baking cookies forever. Feed the monsters with your cookies. Feeling tired? Then hire a worker to bake cookies for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329020/extras/adcb5fd24e38dc50f3874d9b290ce9de.poster.avif?t=1733406088\" width=572 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329020/extras/adcb5fd24e38dc50f3874d9b290ce9de.webm?t=1733406088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329020/extras/adcb5fd24e38dc50f3874d9b290ce9de.mp4?t=1733406088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the cookie monsters grow, they develop stronger jaws. Be careful when choosing upgrades to ensure the best strategy. If you use the prestige system at the right time, you can progress much faster.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this endless journey of growth, fully upgraded cookie monsters will reward you with a stunning visual feast.</p>",
